{"id":46752,"date":[{"year":1938,"month":12,"day":4}],"page":"12","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"儿童园(第17期)","column":"诗歌","genre":"文学作品","count":"186","ytitle":"","mtitle":"难民歌","ftitle":"","authors":["大孩子"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"大孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是难民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃尽了万苦千辛:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挨着饥饿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忍着寒冷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀着苦痛的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接受人家的同情和怜悯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是难民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也曾有可爱的家庭:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勤苦的父亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慈祥的母亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的兄弟姊妹们!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是敌人的炮火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使我们变得孤苦零丁:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村村镇镇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山山城城——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们在到处逃亡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成了没家的流浪人!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是难民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可从不怨天尤人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们懂得爱和憎:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱我们的国家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"憎我们的敌人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们永不忘记——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侵略者的仇恨!"}]}